meanings: (도움, 보탬) [명사] help, assistance, (정부 기관 등의) aid, [동사] help, assist, aid, (보조금을 지급하다) subsidize
[Proper noun] The Mande language of these people.
[Noun] A member of a West African ethnic group located predominantly along the Niger River in Mali, famous for their fishing.
